'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #3283] on 19 January 2001 at 7:52:57 am'!"Change Set:		fixShadowsDate:			19 January 2001Author:			Bob ArningWhen adding a drop shadow or rollover border, force recalculation of fullBounds. Otherwise the shadow may be clipped, especially if rotated"!!Morph methodsFor: 'debug and other' stamp: 'RAA 1/19/2001 07:51'!addMouseActionIndicatorsWidth: anInteger color: aColor	self deleteAnyMouseActionIndicators.	self changed.	self hasRolloverBorder: true.	self setProperty: #rolloverWidth toValue: anInteger@anInteger.	self setProperty: #rolloverColor toValue: aColor.	self layoutChanged.	self changed.! !!Morph methodsFor: 'debug and other' stamp: 'RAA 1/19/2001 07:51'!deleteAnyMouseActionIndicators	self changed.	(self valueOfProperty: #mouseActionIndicatorMorphs ifAbsent: [#()]) do: [ :each |		each deleteWithSiblings		"one is probably enough, but be safe"	].	self removeProperty: #mouseActionIndicatorMorphs.	self hasRolloverBorder: false.	self removeProperty: #rolloverWidth.	self removeProperty: #rolloverColor.	self layoutChanged.	self changed.! !!Morph methodsFor: 'drop shadows' stamp: 'RAA 1/19/2001 07:51'!addDropShadow	self hasDropShadow ifTrue:[^self].	self changed.	self hasDropShadow: true.	self shadowOffset: 3@3.	self layoutChanged.	self changed.! !